explains: n. 失败；加删除线；三击未中出局

sentences.en: He also isn't a strikeout pitcher.
sentences.cn: 他也不是三振型的投手。

sentences.en: Note that strikeout and underline are supported only on Eclipse V3.1.
sentences.cn: 注意，删除线和下划线只在 Eclipse V3.1 上受到支持。

sentences.en: The fact of the matter is he's not a strikeout guy, that's not his style.
sentences.cn: 事实上重点是小民并不是三振型的投手，那本来就不是他的风格。
